query:
INSERT INTO departments (name, description, createdAt, updatedAt) VALUES 
('Engineering', 'Software development, technical architecture, and IT infrastructure', NOW(), NOW()),
('Sales', 'Business development, client acquisition, and revenue generation', NOW(), NOW()),
('Human Resources', 'Employee management, recruitment, and organizational development', NOW(), NOW()),
('Operations', 'Day-to-day business operations and process management', NOW(), NOW()),
('Finance', 'Financial planning, accounting, and budget management', NOW(), NOW()),
('Marketing', 'Brand management, digital marketing, and communications', NOW(), NOW())
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE updatedAt = NOW();
